$interpreted: Roger: The area around here seems safer. Everyone, let's take a quick break.
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Yawn~ NEKO's getting sleepy...Aroma-chan, wake NEKO up when we're about to leave.
PAFF: Okay...NEKO, get some rest.
Nora: (Those mysterious messages, their connection to us...)
Nora: (No, right now, what's important is how to get back. However, can't rule out the possibility that there's no way for us to go back...)
Nora: That singing...is that Miss PAFF?
Nolva: Beautiful...
PAFF: T-thank you...
Nolva: On top of that, I can feel that PAFF really treasures this song.
PAFF: ...This song has always left an impression on me.
PAFF: Even though they're only blurry pieces, when I sing this song, I feel like the "me" from the past still exists.
PAFF: If I think of it that way...I can garner up some courage.
Nolva: ...I think I understand...
Nolva: Even though right now, I have Kittyeyes and others by my side, whenever I wake up from my slumber, I still have this feeling that I'm "no longer myself"...
Nora: (No longer...myself...)
PAFF: Miss Nolva, how about you give it a try?
Nolva: Eh!? I...but I don't know how to sing.
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Hoho~Busted by NEKO live!
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Aww man~~ How dare you teach her how to sing in secret! NEKO wants to be taught as well! Aroma-chan is so sly!
Kittyeyes: Weren't you the one who said you were sleepy...
NEKO#ΦωΦ: This and that are totally different things!!
Roger: Man, you sure are noisy for someone who just woke up. Can't you be more like Miss PAFF?
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Uncle Roger~ Could it be~that you've taken an interest in our adorable Aroma-chan?
Roger: Hey, where did that come from!?
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Aww, you don't have to be shy. It can't be helped; Aroma-chan is just way too cute~
NEKO#ΦωΦ: B-U-T, uncle, you should pay a little more attention to a particular "someone" who's by your side, ya know. It's your duty to make her happy, isn't it~ Ahahaha.
Kittyeyes: NEKO!
Nora: (Duty...NEKO's duty for coming to this world...maybe...it's for something like this...)
Roger: ...Alright, enough joking around.
Nora: Roger has a point. It's about time we leave.
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Ah, right. Let's get going.
Nolva: A-apologies, give me a minute.
Nolva: I just remembered; I haven't taken my medicine for today...
Nolva: It's gone! The medicine Dr. Clovis gave me, it's gone...
Nora: Calm down. Maybe you dropped it nearby. Let's look around.
